<hr>
<strong>WORKS CITED</strong>
<br>
<br>
Add a &#8216;Works Cited&#8217; entry at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body 
of your writing.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	&#34;Title of article.&#34; <em>Name of Publication</em> volume.issue (year of publication): 
	page numbers. Medium of publication.
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	&#34;<span class="hover" title="Title of article">Study Smarter, Not Harder: Setting Goals to Improve Your Academic Performance</span>.&#34; 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Name of Publication">Student Review</span></em> 
	<span class="hover" title="volume">25</span>.<span class="hover" title="issue">5</span> 
	(<span class="hover" title="year of publication">2056</span>): 
	<span class="hover" title="page numbers">10&#45;12</span>. 
	<span class="hover" title="Medium of publication">Print</span>.
</blockquote>
<br>
